---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - telMAX"
  description="How telMAX collects, uses and protects your personal information."
>
  <section class="section bg-green hero-block">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-block__inner">
        <span class="pill">Legal</span>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <article class="prose">
        <p class="updated">Last updated: January 2026</p>
        <p>
          telMAX Inc. ("telMAX", "we", "us") is committed to protecting the
          privacy of our customers and website visitors. This policy explains
          what personal information we collect, how we use it, and the choices
          you have. It is provided as a starting template - please have it
          reviewed by qualified legal counsel before publishing.
        </p>

        <h2>Information we collect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Contact details such as your name, address, email and phone number.</li>
          <li>Account and billing information needed to provide your services.</li>
          <li>Service and network data used to deliver and support your connection.</li>
          <li>Website usage data, including cookies and analytics information.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How we use your information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To provide, install, maintain and support your telMAX services.</li>
          <li>To process payments and manage your account.</li>
          <li>To communicate with you about service, offers and updates.</li>
          <li>To improve our network, website and customer experience.</li>
          <li>To meet legal, regulatory and security obligations.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Sharing your information</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell your personal information. We may share it with service
          providers who help us operate our business, and where required by law.
        </p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Our website uses cookies and similar technologies to keep the site
          working, remember your preferences and understand how the site is used.
          You can control cookies through your browser settings.
        </p>

        <h2>Your choices</h2>
        <p>
          You may request access to, or correction of, the personal information
          we hold about you, and you may opt out of marketing communications at
          any time.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-party services on this website</h2>
        <p>
          To make this website work, a few features send limited data to trusted
          third parties:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Address lookup.</strong> When you type an address to check
            availability, we send the text you enter to a mapping service to
            suggest matching addresses. We do not send your name, email or phone
            number for this lookup.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Web fonts.</strong> We load fonts from a web-font provider,
            which receives your device's IP address as part of serving those
            files.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Bot protection.</strong> Security-sensitive forms, such as
            password reset, use a bot-protection service to confirm you are a
            real person.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          These providers process the data described above under their own
          privacy terms and only to perform the function requested.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact us</h2>
        <p>
          For privacy questions, email <a href="mailto:support@telmax.com" style="text-decoration:underline">support@telmax.com</a>
          or call 1-844-483-5629.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-block { padding-top: clamp(64px, 9vw, 120px); }
</style>
